[OpenVMS Host Option]

Specifies that you want to use the CSRCESRV services (available with z/OS) to compress 
data on output. For example: 

  data _null_;
     file myfile csrc;
     put ... ;
  run;

You cannot use this option with an external file that has a fixed-length record format.

StatementHelp.#cdata:
Executes a SAS statement for observations that meet specific conditions. 

Syntax: 
(1) IF expression THEN statement; 
    <ELSE statement;> 
(2) IF condition;

